<p data-block-id=\"79174376-f7b4-43bf-9409-51587d5d5cfb\"><strong>Jumlah maksimum</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"758dc3fa-4748-4f73-a0d6-36fa3526991f\">50,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"53be8491-4908-453a-a5d6-07b295a1d745\"><strong>Alur persetujuan pengguna</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"9fc57d96-1811-4271-9984-c438ee5fd8bd\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"322b6b6c-0baa-4331-a492-1e4db5e4161b\"><strong>Simpan</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"512384c3-62e3-4205-8bf0-a56cfcc64096\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"6da78b31-6f61-41aa-b043-d0b3a1332ab1\"><strong>Berulang</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"dd17e927-aab6-4a0d-939f-3c8c32ccbd70\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"95e40a43-40e9-4e20-a9b4-601ec6dde5a5\"><strong>Auth &amp; capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"27d33a34-42dc-4add-86ac-c4b62e41db8b\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"f68bc45c-f3eb-4b9b-9510-eba955677edd\"><strong>Partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"db8935ca-499f-4257-a7b0-ef563c3dbb38\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"93e4a4bf-5b68-44bc-969b-9daab4efd8bf\"><strong>Multiple partial capture</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"881cb193-c9d4-4526-bf18-d961b4db41d3\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"bcf224bf-5f0b-4bfd-981a-0bc4adf32ae9\"><strong>Waktu Kedaluwarsa</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"2bfe0e6e-86f5-4994-85c9-cc9b5e94d394\">20 menit</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"398e467a-cb1c-43c6-a507-1954dcc3ce6a\"><strong>Validitas token pembayaran</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"22bf10fb-e449-470e-bc4d-34d458d57c89\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7b5c15f8-bd8e-460e-a26c-3bf7afd7f8ef\"><strong>Waktu penyelesaian</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"5b039613-3cff-407d-b32a-0062f7886a2d\">T+1 Hari</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2273c6c3-56fc-48dc-9e19-342dec55b23f\"><strong>Refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"7979cc7d-0e6f-45b6-8ecc-227307221f01\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"9acdd529-3d07-4041-942d-6dfa8991770b\"><strong>Partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"1054dda9-9a2a-436f-8317-cbc8bf569d59\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"d42a3e1e-04f0-48d4-b37b-cfe6f039850f\"><strong>Multiple partial refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"a56cfd41-e1e8-4242-96fc-1d4123dc3c37\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8d956275-69af-46f8-bf02-6189ff60e463\"><strong>Validitas refund</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"34802364-06f7-4823-9445-3ae7f061262d\">❌</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"e5668c92-7f76-44a7-880d-2c1bbbeaa024\"><strong>Integrasi yang kompatibel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"58c648a3-6c85-49f8-a7b9-549736774f00\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"me0346f1-jposh5-001\">Alur Pembayaran</h2><p data-block-id=\"me043yhf-2u10nt-013\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment%20Flow-LinePay.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" alt=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" title=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"me0wak74-8jjnl5-011\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-wv5uzf-012\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-zu5zwn-013\">Di halaman checkout, pelanggan akhir memilih LINE Pay E-Wallet </p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">Mengarahkan pelanggan akhir ke aplikasi LINE Pay untuk melakukan pembayaran</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">Pelanggan akhir mengonfirmasi jumlah pembayaran dan merchant sudah benar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-fko1j6-022\" data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:82\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-mlzghw-023\">Pelanggan akhir mengklik Bayar untuk mengonfirmasi pembayaran</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"me13cgxb-fuhsts-111\"></p>","SeoTitle":"LINE Pay E-Wallet","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"LINE Pay E-Wallet","Slug":"line-pay-e-wallet","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-i