4\"><strong>การผสานรวมที่เข้ากันได้</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"58c648a3-6c85-49f8-a7b9-549736774f00\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"me0346f1-jposh5-001\">ขั้นตอนการชำระเงิน</h2><p data-block-id=\"me043yhf-2u10nt-013\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment%20Flow-LinePay.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" alt=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" title=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"me0wak74-8jjnl5-011\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-wv5uzf-012\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-zu5zwn-013\">ในหน้าชำระเงิน ลูกค้าปลายทางเลือก LINE Pay E-Wallet </p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">เปลี่ยนเส้นทางลูกค้าปลายทางไปยังแอป LINE Pay เพื่อทำการชำระเงิน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">ลูกค้าปลายทางยืนยันจำนวนเงินที่ชำระและร้านค้าว่าถูกต้อง</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-fko1j6-022\" data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:82\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-mlzghw-023\">ลูกค้าปลายทางคลิก ชำระเงิน เพื่อยืนยันการชำระเงิน</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"me13cgxb-fuhsts-111\"></p>","SeoTitle":"LINE Pay E-Wallet","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"LINE Pay E-Wallet","Slug":"line-pay-e-wallet","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"1f6a388f-d232-430e-9960-0cfd94ee4c96\"><img data-block-id=\"me0waf84-5ara0m-010\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Line_Pay_Hor.svg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt width=\"182\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:182px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1f6a388f-d232-430e-9960-0cfd94ee4c96\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto;\" type=\"spanMark\">LINE Pay es la E-Wallet líder de Tailandia que proporciona una forma conveniente y segura para que los clientes realicen pagos en línea y en la tienda.</span></p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características y Requisitos</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"567\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:567px;width:567px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:299px;\"><col style=\"width:268px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2935c28f-f3ec-48c6-852f-29eb3a78c58f\"><strong>Código de Canal</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"fb4efbbe-19ca-4298-af67-b88b28e2be29\"><code>LINEPAY</code></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"63f6d343-e680-421c-bada-eaa3df5cc57d\"><strong>Moneda</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"a66b31cd-01b5-4621-8ac4-1d535a504374\">THB</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"9f6aa2ff-eaf6-4118-80d3-11c419aa3538\"><strong>Monto mínimo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"15ceb7ca-e8ee-4a3e-b37e-9166d1972c8f\">1</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"79174376-f7b4-43bf-9409-51587d5d5cfb\"><strong>Monto máximo</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"758dc3fa-4748-4f73-a0d6-36fa3526991f\">50,000</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"53be8491-4908-453a-a5d6-07b295a1d745\"><strong>Flujo de aprobación del usuario</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"9fc57d96-1811-4271-9984-c438ee5fd8bd\">REDIRECT</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"322b6b6c-0baa-4331-a492-1e4db5e4161b\"><strong>Guardar</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"512384c3-62e3-4205-8bf0-a56cfcc64096\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"6da78b31-6f61-41aa-b043-d0b3a1332ab1\"><strong>Recurrente</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"dd17e927-aab6-4a0d-939f-3c8c32ccbd70\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"95e40a43-40e9-4e20-a9b4-601ec6dde5a5\"><strong>Autorización y captura</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"27d33a34-42dc-4add-86ac-c4b62e41db8b\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"f68bc45c-f3eb-4b9b-9510-eba955677edd\"><strong>Captura parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"db8935ca-499f-4257-a7b0-ef563c3dbb38\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"93e4a4bf-5b68-44bc-969b-9daab4efd8bf\"><strong>Múltiples capturas parciales</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"881cb193-c9d4-4526-bf18-d961b4db41d3\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"bcf224bf-5f0b-4bfd-981a-0bc4adf32ae9\"><strong>Tiempo de Expiración</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"2bfe0e6e-86f5-4994-85c9-cc9b5e94d394\">20 minutes</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"398e467a-cb1c-43c6-a507-1954dcc3ce6a\"><strong>Validez del token de Pago</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"22bf10fb-e449-470e-bc4d-34d458d57c89\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"7b5c15f8-bd8e-460e-a26c-3bf7afd7f8ef\"><strong>Tiempo de Liquidación</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"5b039613-3cff-407d-b32a-0062f7886a2d\">T+1 Day</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"2273c6c3-56fc-48dc-9e19-342dec55b23f\"><strong>Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"7979cc7d-0e6f-45b6-8ecc-227307221f01\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"9acdd529-3d07-4041-942d-6dfa8991770b\"><strong>Reembolso parcial</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"1054dda9-9a2a-436f-8317-cbc8bf569d59\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"d42a3e1e-04f0-48d4-b37b-cfe6f039850f\"><strong>Múltiples reembolsos parciales</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"a56cfd41-e1e8-4242-96fc-1d4123dc3c37\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"8d956275-69af-46f8-bf02-6189ff60e463\"><strong>Validez del Reembolso</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"34802364-06f7-4823-9445-3ae7f061262d\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"299\"><p data-block-id=\"e5668c92-7f76-44a7-880d-2c1bbbeaa024\"><strong>Integración compatible</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"268\"><p data-block-id=\"58c648a3-6c85-49f8-a7b9-549736774f00\">Payment API, Payment Link</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"me0346f1-jposh5-001\">Flujo de Pago</h2><p data-block-id=\"me043yhf-2u10nt-013\"><video src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/Payment%20Flow-LinePay.mp4\" mediatype=\"video\" alt=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" title=\"Payment Flow-LinePay.mp4\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" data-type=\"media-content\" style=\"display:flex;margin-right:auto;width:640px;height:360px;\" controls=\"true\">null</video></p><ol data-block-id=\"me0wak74-8jjnl5-011\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-wv5uzf-012\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-zu5zwn-013\">En la página de checkout, los clientes finales seleccionan LINE Pay E-Wallet</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">Redirigir a los clientes finales a la aplicación de LINE Pay para realizar el pago</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-9eg6sd-014\" data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:68\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-jww857-015\">Los clientes finales confirman que el monto del pago y el comercio son correctos</p></li><li data-block-id=\"me0wak74-fko1j6-022\" data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:82\"><p data-block-id=\"me0wak74-mlzghw-023\">Los clientes finales hacen clic en Pagar para confirmar el pago</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"me13cgxb-fuhsts-111\"></p>","SeoTitle":"LINE Pay E-Wallet","Description":null}]